{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add additional features to a GeoJSON style source."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"forSourceId","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sourceId","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"features"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Feature","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Feature","preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea"},{"kind":"text","text":"], "},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"sourceId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The identifier of the style source.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"features","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An array of GeoJSON features to be added to the source.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"dataId","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An arbitrary string used to track the given GeoJSON data."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The add operation will be scheduled and applied on a GeoJSON serialization queue.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In order to capture events when actual data is drawn on the map please refer to Events API"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and listen to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onSourceDataLoaded"},{"text":" (optionally pass the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dataId"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter to filter the events)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onMapLoadingError"},{"text":" with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"type = metadata"},{"text":" if data parsing error has occurred.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Partially updating a GeoJSON source is not compatible with using shared cache and generated IDs.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is important to ensure that every feature in the GeoJSON style source, as well as the newly added"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"map-loading-error"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","name":"Note","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dataId"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"source-data-loaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"each batch will be included in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"call, the data ID in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"Throws","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" if there is a problem adding features to the source.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"forSourceId"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"features"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea","text":"Feature","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"], "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"dataId"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"role":"symbol","title":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)","externalID":"s:10MapboxMaps12StyleManagerC24addGeoJSONSourceFeatures11forSourceId8features04dataK0ySS_Say4Turf7FeatureVGSSSgtF","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapboxMaps"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/stylemanager\/addgeojsonsourcefeatures(forsourceid:features:dataid:)"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleManager\/addGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/O